    "body": "I'm ok with 32 bytes.\r\n\r\nSorry, I remembered that my original reason for wanting 256 bytes was erasure coding efficiency, but then I remembered that hash tree chunk size and erasure code chunk size do not need to be the same. So 32 byte shard chunks it is.",
